-$--><div class="flex flex-row"><main class="flex-1 relative py-8 lg:px-12 break-anywhere page-api-block:xl:max-2xl:pr-0 page-api-block:max-w-[1654px] page-api-block:mx-auto"><header class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-6 space-y-3 page-api-block:ml-0"><h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Safety checks</h1></header><div class="[&amp;&gt;*+*]:mt-5 grid whitespace-pre-wrap"><!--$--><h2 id="potential-risks" class="text-3xl font-semibold group relative grid max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 page-api-block:ml-0"><div class="grid grid-area-1-1 relative -ml-6 w-7 border-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-[0] group-focus:opacity-[0] md:group-hover:md:opacity-[1] md:group-focus:md:opacity-[1] [margin-top:_1em]"><a href="#potential-risks" aria-label="Direct link to heading" class="inline-flex h-full items-start dark:text-light/3 dark:shadow-none dark:ring-0 leading-tight"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-3.5 h-[1lh] transition-colors stroke-transparent group-hover:stroke-dark/6 dark:group-hover:stroke-light/5 lg:w-4" height="24" width="24" style="color:currentColor"><path d="M4 9h16M4 15h16M10 3L8 21M16 3l-2 18"></path></svg></a></div><div class="grid-area-1-1 z-[1] [margin-top:_1em]">Potential risks</div></h2><!--/$--><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 page-api-block:ml-0">Each asset listed on Native has specific risk values, shaping how they are supplied and borrowed within the market. It is crucial for the Native community to understand these risks by:</p><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class="list-none space-y-2 [&amp;&gt;li]:relative [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-[2.25ch] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;div_div]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:bg-dark/6 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:absolute [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:left-0 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:w-[1ch] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:h-[1lh] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:[mask-repeat:no-repeat] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:[mask-position:left] dark:[&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:bg-light/6 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circleFilled [&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circle [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-dash [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-squareFilled [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-square [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circleFilled max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 page-api-block:ml-0"><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash">Assessing smart contract security</p><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash">Understanding the risks of centralization</p><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash">Understanding market risks</p><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--></ul><!--/$--><!--$--><div class="rounded-lg straight-corners:rounded-sm ring-1 ring-inset ring-dark/3 flex overflow-hidden flex-col dark:ring-light/2 max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 page-api-block:ml-0"><div role="tablist" class="group/tabs inline-flex flex-row self-stretch after:flex-[1] after:bg-dark-2/1 [&amp;:has(button.active-tab:last-of-type):after]:rounded-bl-md dark:after:bg-dark-1/5"><button role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="tabpanel-1BheHQDz6qZr" id="tab-1BheHQDz6qZr" class="[&amp;:has(+_.active-tab)]:rounded-br-md [.active-tab_+_&amp;]:rounded-bl-md [.active-tab_+_:after]:rounded-br-md inline-block text-sm px-3.5 py-2 transition-[color] font-[500] relative after:transition-colors after:group-hover/tabs:border-transparent after:border-r after:absolute after:left-[unset] after:right-0 after:border-dark/4 after:top-[15%] after:h-[70%] after:w-[1px] last:after:border-transparent hover:text-dark-2 dark:after:border-light/2 dark:hover:text-light-3 truncate max-w-full shrink-0 active-tab text-dark-2 bg-transparent dark:text-light dark:bg-transparent after:[&amp;.active-tab]:border-transparent after:[:has(+_&amp;.active-tab)]:border-transparent after:[:has(&amp;_+)]:border-transparent">Centralization risks</button><button role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabpanel-5g8t19uvLpgk" id="tab-5g8t19uvLpgk" class="[&amp;:has(+_.active-tab)]:rounded-br-md [.active-tab_+_&amp;]:rounded-bl-md [.active-tab_+_:after]:rounded-br-md inline-block text-sm px-3.5 py-2 transition-[color] font-[500] relative after:transition-colors after:group-hover/tabs:border-transparent after:border-r after:absolute after:left-[unset] after:right-0 after:border-dark/4 after:top-[15%] after:h-[70%] after:w-[1px] last:after:border-transparent text-dark-2/7 bg-dark-2/1 dark:bg-dark-1/5 hover:text-dark-2 dark:text-light-3/8 dark:after:border-light/2 dark:hover:text-light-3 truncate max-w-full">Market risks</button></div><div role="tabpanel" id="tabpanel-1BheHQDz6qZr" aria-labelledby="tab-1BheHQDz6qZr" class="p-4"><div class="w-full space-y-6"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 flip-heading-hash">Some tokens have increased risks of centralization, potentially being exposed to a single point of failure in their governance. The counterparty risks, including trust factors, are too high for these assets to guarantee the solvency of the protocol. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 flip-heading-hash">Conversely, some decentralized tokens are not battle-tested and cannot be used as collateral.</p><!--/$--></div></div><div role="tabpanel" id="tabpanel-5g8t19uvLpgk" aria-labelledby="tab-5g8t19uvLpgk" class="p-4 hidden"><div class="w-full space-y-6"><!--$--><h4 id="liquidity-risks" class="text-base font-semibold group relative grid max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 flip-heading-hash"><div class="grid grid-area-1-1 relative -ml-6 w-7 border-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-[0] group-focus:opacity-[0] md:group-hover:md:opacity-[1] md:group-focus:md:opacity-[1] [margin-top:_0.5em]"><a href="#liquidity-risks" aria-label="Direct link to heading" class="inline-flex h-full items-start dark:text-light/3 dark:shadow-none dark:ring-0 leading-snug"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-3.5 h-[1lh] transition-colors stroke-transparent group-hover:stroke-dark/6 dark:group-hover:stroke-light/5 lg:w-4" height="24" width="24" style="color:currentColor"><path d="M4 9h16M4 15h16M10 3L8 21M16 3l-2 18"></path></svg></a></div><div class="grid-area-1-1 z-[1] [margin-top:_0.5em]"><strong class="font-bold">1. Liquidity risks</strong></div></h4><!--/$--><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 flip-heading-hash">Liquidity, determined by on-chain liquidity and trading volume, is critical for the money market’s liquidation process. Liquidity risks can be mitigated through <a class="underline underline-offset-2 text-primary hover:text-primary-700 transition-colors " href="/native/getting-started/lend/safety-checks#supply-cap">supply</a> and <a class="underline underline-offset-2 text-primary hover:text-primary-700 transition-colors " href="/native/getting-started/lend/safety-checks#borrow-cap">borrow caps</a> and by adjusting <a class="underline underline-offset-2 text-primary hover:text-primary-700 transition-colors " href="/native/getting-started/lend/safety-checks#liquidation-threshold-lt">liquidation thresholds</a>. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><h4 id="id-2.-volatility-risks" class="text-base font-semibold group relative grid max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 flip-heading-hash"><div class="grid grid-area-1-1 relative -ml-6 w-7 border-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-[0] group-focus:opacity-[0] md:group-hover:md:opacity-[1] md:group-focus:md:opacity-[1] [margin-top:_0.5em]"><a href="#id-2.-volatility-risks" aria-label="Direct link to heading" class="inline-flex h-full items-start dark:text-light/3 dark:shadow-none dark:ring-0 leading-snug"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-3.5 h-[1lh] transition-colors stroke-transparent group-hover:stroke-dark/6 dark:group-hover:stroke-light/5 lg:w-4" height="24" width="24" style="color:currentColor"><path d="M4 9h16M4 15h16M10 3L8 21M16 3l-2 18"></path></svg></a></div><div class="grid-area-1-1 z-[1] [margin-top:_0.5em]"><strong class="font-bold">2. Volatility risks</strong></div></h4><!--/$--><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 flip-heading-hash">Price volatility can negatively impact the value of collateral. To cover liabilities and ensure the protocol&#x27;s solvency, collateral risk can be mitigated by setting appropriate<a class="underline underline-offset-2 text-primary hover:text-primary-700 transition-colors " href="/native/getting-started/lend/safety-checks#loan-to-value-ltv"> Loan-To-Value (LTV)</a> ratios and liquidation thresholds. The most volatile assets have lower LTVs (35-40%) and lower liquidation thresholds to protect users from sudden price drops that could lead to under-collateralization and liquidation.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class="list-none space-y-2 [&amp;&gt;li]:relative [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-[2.25ch] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;div_div]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:bg-dark/6 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:absolute [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:left-0 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:w-[1ch] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:h-[1lh] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:[mask-repeat:no-repeat] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:[mask-position:left] dark:[&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:bg-light/6 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circleFilled [&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circle [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-dash [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-squareFilled [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-square [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circleFilled max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 flip-heading-hash"><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash"><strong class="font-bold">Least volatile assets</strong>: Stablecoins, WETH, WBTC</p><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class="list-none space-y-2 [&amp;&gt;li]:relative [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-[2.25ch] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;div_div]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:bg-dark/6 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:absolute [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:left-0 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:w-[1ch] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:h-[1lh] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:[mask-repeat:no-repeat] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:[mask-position:left] dark:[&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:bg-light/6 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circleFilled [&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circle [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-dash [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-squareFilled [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-square [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circleFilled max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash"><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash">Highest LTV (70-80%)</p><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash">Highest liquidation threshold (75-88%)</p><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--></ul><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash"><strong class="font-bold">Most Volatile Assets</strong>: Typically have low LTVs (35-40%) and lower liquidation thresholds to protect against sharp price drops.</p><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--></ul><!--/$--><!--$--><h4 id="id-3.-market-capitalization-mcap-risks" class="text-base font-semibold group relative grid max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 flip-heading-hash"><div class="grid grid-area-1-1 relative -ml-6 w-7 border-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-[0] group-focus:opacity-[0] md:group-hover:md:opacity-[1] md:group-focus:md:opacity-[1] [margin-top:_0.5em]"><a href="#id-3.-market-capitalization-mcap-risks" aria-label="Direct link to heading" class="inline-flex h-full items-start dark:text-light/3 dark:shadow-none dark:ring-0 leading-snug"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-3.5 h-[1lh] transition-colors stroke-transparent group-hover:stroke-dark/6 dark:group-hover:stroke-light/5 lg:w-4" height="24" width="24" style="color:currentColor"><path d="M4 9h16M4 15h16M10 3L8 21M16 3l-2 18"></path></svg></a></div><div class="grid-area-1-1 z-[1] [margin-top:_0.5em]"><strong class="font-bold">3. Market capitalization (MCAP) risks</strong></div></h4><!--/$--><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 flip-heading-hash">Market capitalization (MCAP) represents the total value of all coins in circulation, calculated by multiplying the number of coins by the current market price. MCAP is crucial for understanding market size and liquidation potential.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class="list-none space-y-2 [&amp;&gt;li]:relative [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-[2.25ch] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;div_div]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:bg-dark/6 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:absolute [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:left-0 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:w-[1ch] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:h-[1lh] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:[mask-repeat:no-repeat] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:[mask-position:left] dark:[&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:bg-light/6 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circleFilled [&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circle [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-dash [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-squareFilled [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-square [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circleFilled max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 flip-heading-hash"><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash"><strong class="font-bold">Small market cap</strong>: Generally, assets with smaller market caps are less mature and more volatile. Liquidation parameters for these assets are adjusted to mitigate price impact risks.</p><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash"><strong class="font-bold">High market cap</strong>: Indicates a more developed ecosystem with higher liquidity, facilitating liquidations with less impact on prices.</p><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--></ul><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><h2 id="risk-parameters-and-safety-features" class="text-3xl font-semibold group relative grid max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 page-api-block:ml-0"><div class="grid grid-area-1-1 relative -ml-6 w-7 border-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-[0] group-focus:opacity-[0] md:group-hover:md:opacity-[1] md:group-focus:md:opacity-[1] [margin-top:_1em]"><a href="#risk-parameters-and-safety-features" aria-label="Direct link to heading" class="inline-flex h-full items-start dark:text-light/3 dark:shadow-none dark:ring-0 leading-tight"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-3.5 h-[1lh] transition-colors stroke-transparent group-hover:stroke-dark/6 dark:group-hover:stroke-light/5 lg:w-4" height="24" width="24" style="color:currentColor"><path d="M4 9h16M4 15h16M10 3L8 21M16 3l-2 18"></path></svg></a></div><div class="grid-area-1-1 z-[1] [margin-top:_1em]">Risk parameters and safety features</div></h2><!--/$--><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 page-api-block:ml-0">This section define the thresholds and limits for borrowing and collateral to ensure market stability and protect user assets.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><h3 id="loan-to-value-ltv" class="text-2xl font-semibold group relative grid max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 page-api-block:ml-0"><div class="grid grid-area-1-1 relative -ml-6 w-7 border-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-[0] group-focus:opacity-[0] md:group-hover:md:opacity-[1] md:group-focus:md:opacity-[1] [margin-top:_0.75em]"><a href="#loan-to-value-ltv" aria-label="Direct link to heading" class="inline-flex h-full items-start dark:text-light/3 dark:shadow-none dark:ring-0 leading-snug"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-3.5 h-[1lh] transition-colors stroke-transparent group-hover:stroke-dark/6 dark:group-hover:stroke-light/5 lg:w-4" height="24" width="24" style="color:currentColor"><path d="M4 9h16M4 15h16M10 3L8 21M16 3l-2 18"></path></svg></a></div><div class="grid-area-1-1 z-[1] [margin-top:_0.75em]">Loan to Value (LTV)</div></h3><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class="list-none space-y-2 [&amp;&gt;li]:relative [&amp;&gt;li]:ps-[2.25ch] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;div_div]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:bg-dark/6 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:absolute [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:left-0 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:w-[1ch] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:h-[1lh] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:[mask-repeat:no-repeat] [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:[mask-position:left] dark:[&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet]:before:bg-light/6 [&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circleFilled [&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circle [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-dash [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-squareFilled [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-square [&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;_&amp;&gt;li&gt;.bullet:before]:bullet-circleFilled max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 page-api-block:ml-0"><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash">The Loan to Value (LTV) ratio defines the maximum amount that can be borrowed against specific collateral, expressed as a percentage. </p><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash">For example, an LTV of 75% means you can borrow 0.75 ETH worth of assets for every 1 ETH of collateral.</p><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--><!--$--><li class="leading-normal"><div class="bullet text-base"></div><div class="space-y-2 flex flex-col"><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 min-h-[1lh] flip-heading-hash"><button data-testid="annotation-button" aria-label="Open annotation" class="decoration-dotted decoration-1 underline underline-offset-2" type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-:R5m8ddff93bqlta:" data-state="closed">Each asset has its own LTV</button>, which can change with market conditions.</p><!--/$--></div></li><!--/$--></ul><!--/$--><!--$--><h3 id="liquidation-threshold-lt" class="text-2xl font-semibold group relative grid max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 page-api-block:ml-0"><div class="grid grid-area-1-1 relative -ml-6 w-7 border-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-[0] group-focus:opacity-[0] md:group-hover:md:opacity-[1] md:group-focus:md:opacity-[1] [margin-top:_0.75em]"><a href="#liquidation-threshold-lt" aria-label="Direct link to heading" class="inline-flex h-full items-start dark:text-light/3 dark:shadow-none dark:ring-0 leading-snug"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-3.5 h-[1lh] transition-colors stroke-transparent group-hover:stroke-dark/6 dark:group-hover:stroke-light/5 lg:w-4" height="24" width="24" style="color:currentColor"><path d="M4 9h16M4 15h16M10 3L8 21M16 3l-2 18"></path></svg></a></div><div class="grid-area-1-1 z-[1] [margin-top:_0.75em]">Liquidation Threshold (LT)</div></h3><!--/$--><!--$--><p class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto decoration-primary/6 page-api-block:ml-0"><span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>q</mi><mi>u</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>n</mi><mspace width="